Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a story only she and I know about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The story of the secret of this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.91,0:01:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like a pool of light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.16,0:01:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She ran out of the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Praying with all her heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she crossed the shrine gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.02,0:03:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Fish?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.36,0:03:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I wonder if what I saw\Nthat day was just a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, it wasn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That summer day, up in the sky,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.67,0:03:36.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we changed the shape of the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.81,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're expecting very heavy rain shortly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gonna rain again.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it had finally cleared.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,We ran into a typhoon on the island too.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.57,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your safety, please go back inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What a storm it was.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure you don't want any?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks for treating me.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.\NYou saved me.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That was close.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.90,0:06:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I saved someone's life.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.10,Main,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.10,0:06:14.41,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, do they sell beer here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall I get you one?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so expensive!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A grown-up man scrounging on me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is scary.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's raining again.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.64,0:06:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Er... To visit a relative.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts early at my school.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ever need help, contact me.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.90,Main,,0,0,0,,See ya, kid.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Shower's 280 yen for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.03,0:07:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It suddenly started pouring down again...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever learn?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a pain to clean up.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.74,0:07:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.43,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last year's record instances{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.44,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of sudden torrential rain were\Nlargely exceeded this year...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really in college?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's your ID?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.37,0:07:59.95,Main,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.95,0:08:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not stuff for kids.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.96,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sudden downpours expected...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is scary.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got to start saving.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't sit down here, please.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.01,Main,,0,0,0,,1,800 yen all you can drink.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister.\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.61,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything the solicitors say is a lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?\NAre you a minor?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.51,Top,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is scary.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go home.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Never again.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Is he sleeping?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,On the floor?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.57,0:09:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,are you a customer?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,No, sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Is he OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a toy.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.06,0:11:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Er... What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's for you.\NDon't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? But, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You've eaten that for\Ndinner three nights in a row.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that was{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.89,0:11:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the most delicious dinner I've\Nhad in all 16 years of my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,When can we meet again?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,How about the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.67,0:12:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Great! I found a nice café.\NI'll book a table.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,See you, Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye, Ayane.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A grade schooler...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,How lucky. I was hoping to see you.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.92,0:12:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kana.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a ladies' man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you curl your hair?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.33,0:12:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You look great.\NVery lovely.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokyo's amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It should be here.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm Morishima.\NI called earlier.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga, are you in?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.06,0:13:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.27,0:13:14.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, this isn't right.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The new assistant.\NKei told me.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I haven't yet...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Natsumi.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally, someone else to do the grunt work!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You looked at my boobs.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka Morishima.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka. Beautiful name.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you employed here, Natsumi?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanna know about me and Kei?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.67,0:14:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so funny.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like you think.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen a mistress before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, kid.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you lost weight?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.59,0:14:26.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you went out gambling again.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.64,0:14:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You're looking for a job, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what we're working on now.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We write for time-honored\Nand prestigious magazines.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Our next feature is "Urban Legends."
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.65,0:14:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Go and interview people who\Nwitnessed or experienced some.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? But, I...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Any topic will do.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Disappearances, human traffic, etc.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You kids like that kinda stuff, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.12,0:15:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,"The girl who brings sunshine\Nwherever she goes."
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Sunshine girl"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm like that!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's raining so much this year.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.33,Top,,0,0,0,,He ignored me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a demand for that.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, kid.\NYou've got zero initiative.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She's got an interview appointment.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Go along and listen.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Me? Now?!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You're on probation!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,"Probatory period."
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No, really. I can't.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.84,0:15:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, sunshine girls do exist.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And also rain girls.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The first are possessed by a fox god.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The latter by a dragon god.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Dragon god individuals drink a lot.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,They yearn for water.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,They're strong-willed and competitive,\Nbut a bit careless and unreliable.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's me.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.42,0:15:52.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Fox god individuals are hardworking,\Nbut too weak-hearted to be leaders.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Many are beautiful.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Definitely me.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,The weather's off-balance,
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.83,Main,,0,0,0,,so more sunshine and rain girls are born now.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Homeostasis of Gaia theory.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But, we must be careful.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Messing with nature always has a cost.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.28,0:16:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever uses too much weather\Npower gets spirited away.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.71,0:16:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A so-called psychic talked at length\Nabout fantasy novel-like stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"If you use too much power\Nyou'll disappear."
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. That kinda stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather isn't some kind of "power."
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.33,0:16:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, we're aware of that.\NBut, we're providing entertainment.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.87,0:16:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've written\Nso far? You're slow.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.11,0:16:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's not bad.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.73,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, you're hired.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! I didn't say I was...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a live-in job.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.42,0:16:55.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Meals included.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! Please hire me.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.62,Top,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name again?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.25,Top,,0,0,0,,Droll.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm underage, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate Hodaka's hiring.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.99,0:17:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the first meal I shared\Nwith someone since I came to Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is when my new life started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.89,0:18:05.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a small editing company,\Nrun by Mr. Suga and Natsumi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did all the office chores.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.88,0:18:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Starting from Mr. Suga's personal care...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.42,0:18:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Answering the phone, filing receipts,\Ntranscribing interviews.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've written so far?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't mine.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga's out of the office...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.69,0:18:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes I rode around town with\NNatsumi to do some interviews.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,They're looking for a sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hilarious.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.53,Main,,0,0,0,,My sis' friend's a real sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She calls her the day before a date...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not interested.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Then the weather balloon's videosonde\Npicked up something strange.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.99,0:19:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,A swarm of moving objects\Namong the cumulonimbi.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've written?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to buy these when they're on sale.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,He's out of the office...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,This paragraph's crap.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But this ain't bad.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga, wake up. Come on.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My days were hectic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, for the first time\Nsomeone was relying on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those rainy days in Tokyo passed in a flash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.78,0:19:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Rain.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.47,0:19:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Rain. Rain. Rain.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,How's it going, Rain?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Good boy.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an easy job.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.00,0:20:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Just give it a try.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll get paid right away.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Our club is right there.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.96,0:20:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.28,0:20:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Give it a go and earn yourself some bucks.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's right there. Let's go!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.98,0:20:56.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.20,0:21:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Just keep running!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, man.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You were forcing her.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.21,0:21:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you dumb or what?\NWe've made a deal.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.61,0:21:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.55,0:21:35.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the brat that was\Nsquatting in front of our club?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this, payback?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop it.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.18,0:21:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NA toy gun?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are dumb.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.81,0:22:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.57,0:22:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that for?\NTo thank me for that burger?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.05,0:22:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that gun?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.76,0:22:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I found it.\NI thought it was a toy.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.04,0:22:58.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It was like a lucky charm for me.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.57,0:22:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.91,0:23:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You pointed it at someone.\NYou could have killed him.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! You make me sick.\NYou're the worst.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:42.32,0:23:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I got fired from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.06,0:23:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Was it my fault?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.72,0:23:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing to do with that burger.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.55,0:23:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that's why I need a well-paid job.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.40,0:23:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NI shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.55,0:24:06.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:06.30,0:24:07.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a runaway, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.43,0:24:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you can't enjoy Tokyo with this rain.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.72,0:24:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.24,0:24:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:39.67,0:24:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll clear up now.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:41.96,0:24:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.37,0:24:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:13.24,0:25:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A sunshine girl?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:16.73,0:25:18.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Hina.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:18.31,0:25:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:19.18,0:25:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:19.88,0:25:21.18,Main,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:21.18,0:25:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,16.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:23.41,0:25:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Younger than me.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:24.93,0:25:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be 18 next month.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:29.03,0:25:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't look it.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:30.80,0:25:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You should treat me with respect.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:40.22,0:25:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:43.68,0:25:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:33.48,0:26:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, there's a fish.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:34.65,0:26:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Nice.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:37.73,0:26:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say bullshit.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:39.49,0:26:41.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:41.07,0:26:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:45.98,0:26:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Look. Over there.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:48.50,0:26:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't see anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:49.67,0:26:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's there.\NLook harder.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:05.46,0:27:07.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:27:23.20,0:27:29.54,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Kanto region is experiencing\Nrecord-breaking rainfall this summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:27:29.54,0:27:33.07,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been raining continuously for two months.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:27:33.07,0:27:38.52,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The 30 days forecast predicts more\Nheavy rain for another month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:27:38.52,0:27:45.35,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Meteorological Agency said\Nit's an extremely exceptional...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:27:46.39,0:27:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Too expensive?
Dialogue: 1,0:27:48.54,0:27:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:27:49.56,0:27:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, it's amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:01.07,0:28:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,They kinda look like fish.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:04.05,0:28:06.23,Main,,0,0,0,,They fell from the sky?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:06.23,0:28:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But, they left no trace...
Dialogue: 1,0:28:08.90,0:28:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,They instantly disappear.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:10.50,0:28:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:15.59,0:28:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember what the guy\Nwe interviewed said?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:18.36,0:28:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky's a deeper unknown\Nworld than the sea.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:22.57,0:28:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,A cumulonimbus can hold\Nas much water as a whole lake.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:25.98,0:28:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,So, it could as well harbor\Nan uncharted ecosystem.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:29.65,0:28:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Like these fish?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:31.76,0:28:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess.\NAmazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:34.60,0:28:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,If we write about it...
Dialogue: 1,0:28:36.66,0:28:38.11,Main,,0,0,0,,...maybe we can make good money.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:38.11,0:28:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:40.43,0:28:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're starting to sound like Kei.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:42.69,0:28:44.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be a boring grown-up.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:44.94,0:28:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't put off your sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:47.62,0:28:48.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You're going on a date, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:48.86,0:28:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not a date...
Dialogue: 1,0:28:50.48,0:28:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for a job.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:52.44,0:28:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Don't you work here?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:54.62,0:28:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just hanging out.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:01.48,0:29:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not a date, I said.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:05.50,0:29:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:08.66,0:29:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But, she finally stopped talking about you.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:13.35,0:29:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be cruel to meet her now.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:16.15,0:29:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I have the right to see her.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:19.06,0:29:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, you smoke. Don't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:29:22.65,0:29:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:29:23.87,0:29:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,She's got asthma.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:26.16,0:29:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:28.18,0:29:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I quit smoking a while ago.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:31.60,0:29:33.16,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:29:33.16,0:29:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You give a bad impression.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:45.76,0:29:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's raining all the time this year.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:47.98,0:29:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,She can't play outside,\Nand it's bad for her asthma.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:52.68,0:29:55.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for children nowadays.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:55.44,0:29:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We used to have beautiful\Nsprings and summers.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:11.29,0:30:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,They can't live together\Njust the two of them.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:13.69,0:30:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:22.12,0:30:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:24.25,0:30:26.09,Main,,0,0,0,,So, possibly...
Dialogue: 1,0:30:27.19,0:30:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm visiting a girl's home
Dialogue: 1,0:30:30.47,0:30:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the first time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:30:33.97,0:30:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hodaka.\NYou got lost, didn't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:30:36.48,0:30:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No, er... It's not much, but...
Dialogue: 1,0:30:39.56,0:30:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, thank you. Come on in.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:43.48,0:30:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:44.49,0:30:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:49.72,0:30:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you have lunch?
Dialogue: 1,0:30:51.78,0:30:54.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Not yet. But, it's OK.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:54.49,0:30:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sit there and relax.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:56.50,0:30:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I use these?
Dialogue: 1,0:30:58.00,0:30:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:59.27,0:31:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:13.57,0:31:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you live alone?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:16.17,0:31:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,With my younger brother.\NWe had some problems.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:19.55,0:31:21.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Problems?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:21.02,0:31:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,How about you?\NWhy did you run away?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:25.44,0:31:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I found it suffocating to live with my parents.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:28.03,0:31:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And in that town.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:31.06,0:31:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:40.41,0:31:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you go back?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:44.26,0:31:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:46.40,0:31:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:49.05,0:31:51.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:51.55,0:31:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:52.78,0:31:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot the spring onions!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:58.61,0:32:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you like living in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:00.99,0:32:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Er... Oh.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:02.56,0:32:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 1,0:32:04.52,0:32:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like I'm suffocating anymore.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:06.19,0:32:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:08.65,0:32:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:19.57,0:32:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:21.68,0:32:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:22.58,0:32:23.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the train.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:27.74,0:32:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:29.86,0:32:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a real sunshine girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:33.44,0:32:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You can clear up the sky just by praying.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:35.59,0:32:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:36.71,0:32:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you need a job?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:39.03,0:32:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I do. But, I can't charge people for that.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:42.15,0:32:46.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're cut out for\Nworking in a club like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:47.88,0:32:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:49.54,0:32:50.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:50.87,0:32:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking at anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:52.41,0:32:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:54.74,0:32:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't 5,000 yen too expensive?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:57.12,0:33:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we do 3,000 yen, then?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:00.51,0:33:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Considering living expenses, though...
Dialogue: 1,0:33:03.62,0:33:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we need some graphics.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:05.29,0:33:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw them.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:07.64,0:33:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this? A hippo?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:10.01,0:33:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a frog.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:11.40,0:33:12.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:14.21,0:33:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 1,0:33:15.81,0:33:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll upload it.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:17.28,0:33:17.86,Main,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:17.86,0:33:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:19.23,0:33:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm home.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:21.12,0:33:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like some sardines...
Dialogue: 1,0:33:25.00,0:33:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:25.96,0:33:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the boy on the bus!
Dialogue: 1,0:33:29.75,0:33:31.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know each other?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:31.31,0:33:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, this is my brother Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:33.56,0:33:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Nagi, this is Hodaka.\NHe's my business partner.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:38.16,0:33:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got a request!
Dialogue: 1,0:33:40.09,0:33:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You've already uploaded it?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:41.66,0:33:44.94,Main,,0,0,0,,They want good weather for a flea market.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:44.94,0:33:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:46.17,0:33:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!\NAm I really gonna do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:49.17,0:33:51.67,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Widespread rain tomorrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:33:50.94,0:33:52.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gonna rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:52.57,0:33:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the whole point.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:54.57,0:33:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is that guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:55.98,0:33:57.18,Top,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:57.18,0:33:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:58.26,0:33:59.93,Main,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 1,0:34:02.93,0:34:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Please use this.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:11.08,0:34:12.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I won't.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:12.14,0:34:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got another secret weapon for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:23.94,0:34:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, don't need it.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:25.54,0:34:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,0:34:29.54,0:34:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Who called those weirdos?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:32.31,0:34:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We thought it might bring good luck.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:40.41,0:34:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:43.52,0:34:45.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 1,0:34:45.85,0:34:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Water, Hina?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:47.24,0:34:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want a candy?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:49.71,0:34:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell them to go home.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:51.38,0:34:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:51.97,0:34:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky's clearing up.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:53.05,0:34:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:05.24,0:35:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It cleared up.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:05.24,0:35:08.25,Top,,0,0,0,,It's been ages, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:08.25,0:35:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:08.25,0:35:10.75,Top,,0,0,0,,Finally, after so long.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:10.75,0:35:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:12.46,0:35:14.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:14.25,0:35:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:15.76,0:35:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're awesome, guys.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:17.50,0:35:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a real sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:19.26,0:35:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:20.82,0:35:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're great.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:22.26,0:35:23.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:23.72,0:35:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:25.26,0:35:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's 20,000 yen.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:27.27,0:35:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's too much.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:28.30,0:35:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You get a bonus because you're cute.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:31.22,0:35:35.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.\NWe'll sell a lot more now.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:44.55,0:35:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yaay!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:46.24,0:35:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:47.28,0:35:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel I can do this.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:48.50,0:35:50.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool! Let's make money with the weather.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:50.78,0:35:52.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:36:43.13,0:36:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human mind works in mysterious ways.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:45.64,0:36:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just need to see the sun shining\Nin the morning to feel energized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:50.83,0:36:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A blue sky makes you feel happy you're alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:54.55,0:36:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It makes you feel more in love\Nwith that someone by your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:58.61,0:37:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a once in a lifetime event.\NI wanna wear white under a blue sky.
Dialogue: 1,0:37:02.15,0:37:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,To watch the meteor shower.
Dialogue: 1,0:37:03.86,0:37:06.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It never wins on rainy days!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:06.45,0:37:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I've worked hard in that\Nsweatshop just for today!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:09.29,0:37:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to play outside.
Dialogue: 1,0:37:12.04,0:37:16.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone had their own reason\Nto pursue sunshine in rainy Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:16.96,0:37:21.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina was able to clear only\Nsmall spots for a brief time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:21.02,0:37:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, the sky would always\Nanswer her prayers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:24.26,0:37:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was really the "100% sunshine girl."{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:43.01,0:37:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like the whole town was dressing up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:47.41,0:37:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a wonderful world\NI was born in, I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:52.91,0:37:54.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Smile, please.
Dialogue: 1,0:37:54.91,0:37:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Keep going!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:56.92,0:37:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, there's more!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:58.92,0:38:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Kawaii... kawaii...
Dialogue: 1,0:38:01.42,0:38:03.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 1,0:38:03.17,0:38:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:04.17,0:38:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:05.17,0:38:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:06.18,0:38:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:07.18,0:38:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:38:08.09,0:38:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:09.26,0:38:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're really influenced by the weather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:38:13.13,0:38:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized how much the human\Nheart is connected with the sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:38:23.03,0:38:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:28.05,0:38:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:35.79,0:38:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it canceled due to rain?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:35.79,0:38:38.47,Top,,0,0,0,,It's past noon.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:38.47,0:38:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,When does it start?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:39.79,0:38:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I've changed my clothes to come here.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:41.90,0:38:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we go home?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:43.13,0:38:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:45.94,0:38:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I've read online that the\N"100% sunshine girl" is amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:50.51,0:38:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But, this is such a big event.
Dialogue: 1,0:38:53.05,0:38:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to rely on that?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:55.90,0:39:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's going to rain all week.\NWe won't be able to postpone it.
Dialogue: 1,0:39:00.71,0:39:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,In this situation,
Dialogue: 1,0:39:03.21,0:39:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,we're even ready to rely on a charm.
Dialogue: 1,0:39:51.71,0:39:54.13,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Jingu Gaien fireworks{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:39:54.13,0:39:57.37,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will start at 7 p.m. as scheduled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:40:34.82,0:40:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in love.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:37.91,0:40:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,With this sunshine girl job.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:41.23,0:40:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I finally found my role in life.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:45.82,0:40:47.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:47.17,0:40:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe not.\NOr maybe not not.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:50.62,0:40:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe not not...?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:53.51,0:40:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:55.18,0:40:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too serious.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:58.36,0:41:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:07.48,0:41:10.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weather is a mystery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:10.19,0:41:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way the sky looks can move you so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:15.32,0:41:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina really moves my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:37.62,0:41:43.23,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yesterday's Jingu Gaien fireworks\Nwere blessed with miraculous sunshine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:43.23,0:41:47.03,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, strong rain is back again\Ntoday, just like a backlash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:47.03,0:41:51.55,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The temperature in the capital is\Nnow 21°C, much lower than average.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:51.55,0:41:54.27,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's unusually chilly for August.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:54.27,0:41:56.24,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make sure you wear a light jacket...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:56.24,0:41:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my first company of choice.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:57.57,0:41:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my first company of choice.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:58.91,0:42:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my first company of choice.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:01.91,0:42:05.06,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful not to catch a cold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:05.06,0:42:09.42,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Record rainfall and low temperatures\Nare driving food prices up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:09.42,0:42:13.92,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lettuce is three times more expensive than last year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:18.19,0:42:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, that project? Right,\Nwe've put it on hold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:22.47,0:42:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, we're not going ahead with it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:24.93,0:42:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:26.88,0:42:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. OK.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:27.74,0:42:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best,\Nso please call us again.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:41.60,0:42:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:42:56.10,0:42:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, this is the Mamiya household.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:58.08,0:43:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's Keisuke.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:00.40,0:43:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry to rush you.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:01.99,0:43:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Regarding the visit...
Dialogue: 1,0:43:04.85,0:43:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You're late, Kei.\NIt's an important interview.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:09.22,0:43:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Are we in a bad mood?\NNo luck with work?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:12.20,0:43:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's Hodaka?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:15.13,0:43:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Busy with his other job?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:17.61,0:43:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,He's neglecting work lately.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:19.32,0:43:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Just let him be.\NWe're not that busy.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:22.49,0:43:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,He took in that cat.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:24.53,0:43:25.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You did the same with him.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:25.83,0:43:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:26.78,0:43:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You helped him because he\Nreminded you of yourself.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:31.33,0:43:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,How much are you paying him?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:35.76,0:43:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Only 30,000 yen?\NThat's so low.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:38.45,0:43:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope. It's 3,000 yen.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:40.43,0:43:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:41.81,0:43:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? 3,000 yen a month?\NThat's exploitation.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:45.21,0:43:46.11,Top,,0,0,0,,Look ahead.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:45.67,0:43:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get sued.\NActually, I'll report you.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:50.85,0:43:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,He gets free food and accommodation,
Dialogue: 1,0:43:54.59,0:43:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,and the company pays his phone bills.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:56.86,0:43:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:59.73,0:44:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's got an extra job.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:04.59,0:44:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.\NIt's really cleared up.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:08.37,0:44:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You kids are amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:10.63,0:44:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a shame you're quitting.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:12.79,0:44:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She was caught on camera.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:13.88,0:44:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We got flooded with requests.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:16.88,0:44:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't cope.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:18.86,0:44:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll do a last one then stop for a while.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:23.59,0:44:26.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She looks tired, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:28.28,0:44:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Got guests, Granny?
Dialogue: 1,0:44:30.21,0:44:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:31.39,0:44:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I came to help.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:33.40,0:44:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Very young guests.\NAre you Granny's friends?
Dialogue: 1,0:44:37.37,0:44:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:38.40,0:44:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I've asked for nice weather\Non my husband's first anniversary.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:41.66,0:44:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It stopped raining, in fact.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:52.08,0:44:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be hard for him\Nto come back if it was raining.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:55.63,0:44:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,"Come back"?
Dialogue: 1,0:44:56.80,0:45:00.92,Main,,0,0,0,,They say the dead come back\Nfrom the sky around August 15.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:01.48,0:45:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,So, he died a year ago?
Dialogue: 1,0:45:05.53,0:45:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:06.42,0:45:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom too.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:10.38,0:45:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You lost your mother last year?
Dialogue: 1,0:45:14.16,0:45:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:14.94,0:45:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Light a welcoming fire for her.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:18.45,0:45:20.94,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll protect you.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:20.94,0:45:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:26.76,0:45:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,He'll follow the smoke and come back.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:30.95,0:45:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 1,0:45:32.73,0:45:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,From heaven.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:35.16,0:45:39.01,Main,,0,0,0,,There's always been\Nanother world, up in the sky.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:43.64,0:45:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently, this is what\Nthe Weather Maiden saw.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:47.97,0:45:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a mysterious painting.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:50.12,0:45:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Flying fish in the sky.\NAnd even a dragon.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:52.77,0:45:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:54.23,0:45:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:45:56.25,0:46:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The "Weather Maiden"\Nwas like a shaman, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:00.23,0:46:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:02.56,0:46:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Was she like a shaman?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:05.74,0:46:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:07.74,0:46:12.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Fixing the weather is the\NWeather Maiden's work.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:12.49,0:46:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Fixing it?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:14.46,0:46:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a con.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:15.66,0:46:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Like this year's abnormal weather?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:19.13,0:46:22.75,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing abnormal about that.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:22.75,0:46:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,They say "in recorded history,"
Dialogue: 1,0:46:28.91,0:46:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,but when did records begin?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:31.65,0:46:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,100 years ago at best.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:33.31,0:46:36.27,Main,,0,0,0,,How old do you think this is?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:36.27,0:46:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,800 years old.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:37.88,0:46:38.77,Main,,0,0,0,,800?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:40.27,0:46:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:45.15,0:46:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The weather changes on a whim.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:48.65,0:46:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Regardless of human needs.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:50.91,0:46:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't even tell what's\Nthe norm and what isn't.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:53.84,0:46:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,We're only allowed to stay temporarily
Dialogue: 1,0:46:57.16,0:47:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,in the space between the sky and earth,
Dialogue: 1,0:47:00.89,0:47:04.92,Main,,0,0,0,,clinging hard not to be shaken off.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:04.92,0:47:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We used to be well aware of this in the past.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:10.70,0:47:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But, there's a thin thread\Nlinking us humans and the sky.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:17.64,0:47:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The Weather Maiden.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:20.30,0:47:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,A special girl who can take in people's\Nwishes and deliver them to the sky.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:27.49,0:47:33.49,Main,,0,0,0,,In ancient times, there was one\Nin every village and every country.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:33.49,0:47:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Kei. It sounds like the sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:35.86,0:47:39.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to\Nlisten to my grandpa?
Dialogue: 1,0:47:39.33,0:47:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It all sounds pretty far-fetched.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:42.29,0:47:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a very interesting story.\NWe're thankful.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:45.57,0:47:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But, everything comes at a price.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:51.25,0:47:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,A tragic fate awaits the Weather Maiden.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:59.35,0:48:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:02.26,0:48:04.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Your turn.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:05.28,0:48:07.67,Top,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:07.00,0:48:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for keeping Granny company.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:09.41,0:48:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We're actually here because of work.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:11.86,0:48:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Join us, Granny.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:14.59,0:48:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,They're having fun.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:16.36,0:48:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,How old are you guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:48:17.73,0:48:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm 16. She's...
Dialogue: 1,0:48:21.96,0:48:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,She said it's her birthday next week.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:24.92,0:48:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? You've gotta buy her a present.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:29.55,0:48:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Come eat some watermelon.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:31.69,0:48:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yaay!
Dialogue: 1,0:48:32.72,0:48:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:39.13,0:48:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 1,0:48:49.02,0:48:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang.
Dialogue: 1,0:48:55.25,0:48:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez. Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:48:58.90,0:49:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:15.84,0:49:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know she was a minor, I swear.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:21.18,0:49:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not about that?
Dialogue: 1,0:49:23.45,0:49:26.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you it wasn't.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:26.01,0:49:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You made us run for nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:28.36,0:49:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That's you, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:49:31.96,0:49:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us about this boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:49:38.76,0:49:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,A high school boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:49:41.70,0:49:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe he picked up by chance\Nthe gun Shibata threw away.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:46.64,0:49:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,In that case, he might have posted about it.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:52.07,0:49:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Online, you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:49:54.64,0:49:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Kids write all sorts of stuff\Non social networks nowadays.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:15.44,0:50:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Nagi!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:17.74,0:50:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Nagi!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:17.74,0:50:20.24,Top,,0,0,0,,You're the best.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:23.86,0:50:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A ring. Definitely.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:25.75,0:50:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Isn't it too serious?
Dialogue: 1,0:50:28.89,0:50:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's for my sister's birthday, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:50:31.14,0:50:34.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I've asked another woman\Nfor reference, but...
Dialogue: 1,0:50:34.26,0:50:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What I'd like to get?
Dialogue: 1,0:50:36.12,0:50:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hugs and kisses. Cash.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:37.98,0:50:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,A decent boyfriend. And a job.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:40.59,0:50:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't helpful at all.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:43.01,0:50:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A ring...
Dialogue: 1,0:50:43.55,0:50:45.18,Top,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:45.18,0:50:46.52,Top,,0,0,0,,See you, Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:48.18,0:50:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You're in love with Hina, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:50:50.52,0:50:51.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:50:51.56,0:50:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Er, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:53.83,0:50:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it is?
Dialogue: 1,0:50:56.03,0:50:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Being ambivalent is\Nthe worst thing for a man.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:59.98,0:51:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:51:01.40,0:51:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Be clear before you start dating and\Nbe ambiguous later. It's the basics.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:08.04,0:51:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I call you Nagi Sempai?
Dialogue: 1,0:51:13.44,0:51:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina's been working all\Nthe time since Mom died.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:17.27,0:51:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She's been doing it for me,
Dialogue: 1,0:51:19.80,0:51:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,because I'm still a kid.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:23.31,0:51:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I want her to do more teenage-like stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:27.23,0:51:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're the right guy, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:32.31,0:51:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:37.32,0:51:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Er, do you think she'll like it?
Dialogue: 1,0:51:41.32,0:51:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:51:43.86,0:51:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It took you three hours to choose it.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:46.58,0:51:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If it were I, I'd be very happy to receive it.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:50.00,0:51:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:56.48,0:51:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow's sunshine girl job will be our last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:52:00.22,0:52:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A man requested good weather\Nat the park for his daughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:52:06.73,0:52:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:52:08.60,0:52:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll give Hina the ring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:52:22.01,0:52:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Daddy, do it again.\NOne more time!
Dialogue: 1,0:52:24.95,0:52:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:27.87,0:52:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 1,0:52:32.68,0:52:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:33.96,0:52:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad for your back.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:35.96,0:52:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why you, Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:38.25,0:52:40.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you know this was my job?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:40.53,0:52:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You knew and said nothing?\NActually, you have a daughter?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:44.97,0:52:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm stunned.\NToday's forecast was 100% rain.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:51.93,0:52:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,My daughter has asthma.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:54.59,0:52:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She lives with her granny,
Dialogue: 1,0:52:57.39,0:53:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,who won't let me see her on rainy days.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:01.02,0:53:04.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing can beat a gorgeous blue sky.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:04.04,0:53:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you're Hodaka's boss.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:06.94,0:53:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I also saved his life.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:09.45,0:53:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Why does she treat you like a little boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:11.64,0:53:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina's two years older than me.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:14.50,0:53:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? 16, 17, 18. Same stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:18.29,0:53:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:18.29,0:53:19.41,Top,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:19.41,0:53:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 1,0:53:20.76,0:53:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys!
Dialogue: 1,0:53:24.01,0:53:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna be in trouble?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:27.33,0:53:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Does Natsumi know you're married?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:30.01,0:53:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up with you guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:36.22,0:53:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka thought you were my...
Dialogue: 1,0:53:39.52,0:53:40.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Mistress?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:42.03,0:53:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell me you were uncle and niece.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:45.66,0:53:48.09,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a disgusting fantasy.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:48.09,0:53:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You're dirty-minded.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:50.45,0:53:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:56.04,0:53:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You looked at my boobs.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:57.40,0:53:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 1,0:53:58.54,0:54:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsumi!
Dialogue: 1,0:54:00.55,0:54:02.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Moka!
Dialogue: 1,0:54:02.53,0:54:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I made a garland. It's for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:05.52,0:54:07.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:54:07.05,0:54:08.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Come here, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:08.55,0:54:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,My sempai's calling me.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:13.21,0:54:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka's hilarious.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:14.70,0:54:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,He's such a kid.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:17.25,0:54:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they're similar?
Dialogue: 1,0:54:20.02,0:54:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka and Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 1,0:54:21.20,0:54:22.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:22.10,0:54:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Kei ran away from home and came\Nto Tokyo when he was a teen.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:25.85,0:54:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,He met his future wife\Nand fell in love big time.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:29.81,0:54:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But, she died in an accident some years ago.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:33.23,0:54:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,He's still in love with her.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:37.57,0:54:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been dying to meet you for so long, Hina.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:40.84,0:54:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,The 100% sunshine girl.\NYou're amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:43.90,0:54:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a skill like that\Non my resume. I hate looking for a job.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:47.93,0:54:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I was still in high school too.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:50.46,0:54:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to be a grown-up instead.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:56.28,0:54:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:57.37,0:55:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Good to see you're OK.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:00.97,0:55:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I was actually a bit worried.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:12.17,0:55:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you tired, Moka?
Dialogue: 1,0:55:14.37,0:55:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, take a breath.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:15.85,0:55:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:19.80,0:55:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Let's play!
Dialogue: 1,0:55:21.53,0:55:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 1,0:55:23.00,0:55:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll leave now.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:25.77,0:55:29.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to spend more time with Nagi!
Dialogue: 1,0:55:29.13,0:55:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go to dinner together?
Dialogue: 1,0:55:31.26,0:55:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:55:32.39,0:55:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go eat with Moka. Is it OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:55:35.80,0:55:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:36.22,0:55:37.52,Top,,0,0,0,,Yaay!
Dialogue: 1,0:55:37.52,0:55:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, take Hina home.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:40.81,0:55:42.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:44.07,0:55:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing the sunshine today!
Dialogue: 1,0:55:49.20,0:55:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:50.07,0:55:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I made you happy.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:07.47,0:56:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my god.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:56:09.36,0:56:12.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my god, Oh my god, Oh my god.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:56:14.19,0:56:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, possibly this is gonna be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:56:17.39,0:56:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the first time I tell a girl I love her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:56:28.90,0:56:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:29.56,0:56:30.45,Top,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:30.45,0:56:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:30.89,0:56:31.74,Top,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:32.24,0:56:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:56:33.08,0:56:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:34.82,0:56:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What were you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:56:40.36,0:56:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you know...
Dialogue: 1,0:56:46.25,0:56:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 1,0:56:58.17,0:56:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,0:57:04.87,0:57:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,0:57:06.34,0:57:07.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 1,0:57:36.33,0:57:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I became a sunshine girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:57:39.61,0:57:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...last year, on that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:57:51.00,0:57:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I prayed for good weather\Nall day long the day before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:57:55.24,0:57:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to have one last walk\Nunder the sun with my mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:58:05.22,0:58:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looked like a pool of light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:58:09.11,0:58:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Praying with all my heart,\NI crossed the shrine gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:58:26.20,0:58:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I came around,\NI was lying on the roof floor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:58:29.65,0:58:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the sky was clear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:58:39.85,0:58:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 1,0:58:42.11,0:58:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,that's when I got connected to the sky.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:51.51,0:58:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Connected to the sky?
Dialogue: 1,0:58:57.29,0:58:59.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay in there, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:01.78,0:59:04.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Police. Sorry for the late visit.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:04.37,0:59:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:05.52,0:59:08.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you've never seen him?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:08.62,0:59:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,He's been seen many times around here.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:13.89,0:59:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know him.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:15.91,0:59:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What has he done?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:17.47,0:59:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We want to ask him some questions.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:20.19,0:59:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a runaway.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:22.40,0:59:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,His parents filed a missing person's report.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:26.11,0:59:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, you're living alone\Nwith your little brother, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:31.56,0:59:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:32.31,0:59:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a bit of a problem too.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:35.64,0:59:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Without a guardian, you...
Dialogue: 1,0:59:37.64,0:59:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 1,0:59:38.55,0:59:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't bother anyone.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:45.36,0:59:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:46.68,0:59:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll come back tomorrow\Nwith the social service.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:51.31,0:59:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What can I do?\NThey'll separate us!
Dialogue: 1,1:00:08.46,1:00:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka! The police were...
Dialogue: 1,1:00:10.52,1:00:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. Go home,\NI'll come later.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:13.58,1:00:17.02,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Temperatures have fallen sharply after sunset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:00:17.02,1:00:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 1,1:00:18.52,1:00:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Surprised by my new look?
Dialogue: 1,1:00:20.09,1:00:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in disguise.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:23.02,1:00:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,The police came to my office.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:25.94,1:00:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,They're treating it like a kidnapping.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:29.49,1:00:32.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I denied any involvement,\Nbut they suspect me.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:33.10,1:00:35.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Take it.\NIt's your severance pay.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:36.32,1:00:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't come back to the office.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:38.27,1:00:40.51,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll arrest me.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:43.44,1:00:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I filed for custody of my daughter.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:46.18,1:00:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a delicate time, sorry.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:50.12,1:00:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:53.61,1:00:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Then everything will go back to normal.
Dialogue: 1,1:00:56.63,1:01:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be best for everyone.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:01.96,1:01:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's time to grow up, kid.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:13.61,1:01:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't stay here anymore.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:16.18,1:01:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But, where are you...
Dialogue: 1,1:01:18.25,1:01:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 1,1:01:20.87,1:01:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Anywhere will do.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:22.31,1:01:23.74,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm with you.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:25.08,1:01:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you'd better go\Nhome before you get caught.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:29.47,1:01:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got a place to go back to.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:31.78,1:01:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:35.48,1:01:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:39.19,1:01:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:42.51,1:01:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:50.12,1:01:54.83,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A heavy rain special warning has\Njust been issued in the Tokyo area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:01:54.83,1:01:58.27,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It could be the heaviest rainfall in decades.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:01:58.27,1:02:01.03,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch out for floods in lowland areas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:01.03,1:02:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,A sudden typhoon-strength\Nlow-pressure system...
Dialogue: 1,1:02:04.08,1:02:08.03,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}River flooding. Increasing danger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:08.03,1:02:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's overflowing!
Dialogue: 1,1:02:09.78,1:02:12.79,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,Keep calm and walk slowly towards the exit.
Dialogue: 1,1:02:12.79,1:02:16.79,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Namboku Line Akabane-Iwabuchi\NStation, Shibuya Metro Station...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:16.79,1:02:19.79,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several flights canceled at Haneda Airport.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:19.79,1:02:22.55,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over 6 inches of rain in an hour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:22.55,1:02:25.05,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heavy flooding in many areas of Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:23.86,1:02:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 1,1:02:25.05,1:02:29.55,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kita Ward, Arakawa Ward, Taito Ward,\NSumida Ward, Shibuya Ward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:29.55,1:02:31.56,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may get stranded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:32.36,1:02:34.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,1:02:34.06,1:02:36.29,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's unusually cold for August.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:36.29,1:02:39.06,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The temperature in Tokyo has fallen below 10°C.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:39.06,1:02:41.12,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cumulonimbi keep gathering above Tokyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:41.12,1:02:44.31,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In just an hour, it's like a different season.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:44.31,1:02:45.07,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:45.07,1:02:49.18,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A heavy rain special warning has\Nbeen issued in the Tokyo area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:49.18,1:02:52.09,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The low-pressure system over the Kanto region...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:52.09,1:02:55.08,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of a stream of cold air\Nover Kanto, very unstable weather...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:55.77,1:02:59.08,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More heavy rain in central Japan even after dawn...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:02:59.08,1:03:03.16,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This abnormal weather will continue for a few weeks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:03:03.16,1:03:07.09,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This abnormal weather is unprecedented\Nand extremely dangerous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:03:14.63,1:03:21.48,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Due to transportation delays,\NYamanote Line trains are suspended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:03:21.48,1:03:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 1,1:03:22.95,1:03:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get off.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:24.28,1:03:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Mom to pick us up.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:25.98,1:03:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's freezing.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:26.79,1:03:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 1,1:03:28.27,1:03:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's look for a place to sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:32.46,1:03:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we're fully booked.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:35.87,1:03:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have a reservation?
Dialogue: 1,1:03:37.62,1:03:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,We're full.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:39.12,1:03:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only the three of you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:03:40.62,1:03:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have ID?
Dialogue: 1,1:03:43.13,1:03:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't accept unaccompanied minors.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:44.88,1:03:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of money.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:47.11,1:03:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no place for kids.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:50.30,1:03:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 1,1:03:52.14,1:03:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you runaways?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:04:02.72,1:04:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina, Hodaka. Look!
Dialogue: 1,1:04:05.86,1:04:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 1,1:05:01.36,1:05:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina is connected with the sky...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:05:18.22,1:05:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 1,1:05:22.09,1:05:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey Kei, it's snowing in August.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:25.09,1:05:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The world's finally gone crazy.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:28.94,1:05:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 1,1:05:29.98,1:05:33.74,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's unbelievable, but it's snowing here in Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:05:33.74,1:05:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Kei, wake up.\NYou'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:37.54,1:05:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Asuka.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:41.69,1:05:44.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Asuka. You too, Kei. Smile.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:50.34,1:05:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Brr.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:51.76,1:05:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You look like an old man, Kei.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:55.12,1:05:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, once you grow old
Dialogue: 1,1:05:59.10,1:06:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,you can't switch your priorities anymore.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:03.96,1:06:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NWhere's Hodaka?
Dialogue: 1,1:06:07.04,1:06:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You kicked him out?
Dialogue: 1,1:06:08.77,1:06:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 1,1:06:09.67,1:06:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, the police showed up.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:12.04,1:06:14.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got to protect myself.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:14.96,1:06:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you smoked a pack of cigarettes\Nand got drunk because you felt guilty.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:19.28,1:06:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so uncool, meow.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:21.79,1:06:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Even Rain's saying it.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:23.79,1:06:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Really uncool.\NSo last century.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:26.50,1:06:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you stay away?\NYou smell old.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:28.98,1:06:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're uncool too.\NWhat's her name... Hina?
Dialogue: 1,1:06:33.05,1:06:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,If the story about\Nthe Weather Maiden being...
Dialogue: 1,1:06:36.39,1:06:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...a human sacrifice is true,\Nthen one day she'll...
Dialogue: 1,1:06:39.47,1:06:40.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that's...
Dialogue: 1,1:06:40.80,1:06:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I have done, then?
Dialogue: 1,1:06:43.30,1:06:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get so uptight.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:44.81,1:06:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just bullshit.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:47.53,1:06:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if it was true...
Dialogue: 1,1:06:53.67,1:06:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,If you could fix this crazy weather\Nwith one human sacrifice,
Dialogue: 1,1:06:57.58,1:06:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:00.38,1:07:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone would.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:03.76,1:07:08.40,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A heavy rain and heavy snow\Nwarning has been issued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:07:08.40,1:07:10.33,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go out if it's not strictly necessary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:07:11.13,1:07:14.34,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please follow local government\Nevacuation instructions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:07:13.77,1:07:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You kids.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:16.01,1:07:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to walk around unsupervised.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:18.85,1:07:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all siblings?
Dialogue: 1,1:07:20.67,1:07:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 1,1:07:21.79,1:07:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:23.70,1:07:26.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a college student.\NThey're my younger brothers.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:27.12,1:07:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:29.02,1:07:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you show me your ID?
Dialogue: 1,1:07:30.64,1:07:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have it on me.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:32.86,1:07:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's him.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:34.80,1:07:38.36,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He may be carrying a gun. Be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:07:38.36,1:07:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,And you? Are you in high school?\NThat's a big backpack.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:42.92,1:07:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you remove your hood?
Dialogue: 1,1:07:46.79,1:07:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:48.12,1:07:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Run away.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:51.13,1:07:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 1,1:07:52.96,1:07:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:07:56.05,1:07:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 1,1:07:57.12,1:07:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 1,1:07:59.30,1:08:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Resisting arrest.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:04.60,1:08:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:05.32,1:08:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop struggling.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:07.75,1:08:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:10.21,1:08:11.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:14.15,1:08:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:15.93,1:08:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:33.25,1:08:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:39.10,1:08:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:41.13,1:08:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:41.80,1:08:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:43.89,1:08:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sempai.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:54.07,1:08:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's 28,000 yen a night.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:57.23,1:08:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,28,000 yen. Can you pay?
Dialogue: 1,1:08:59.31,1:09:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes. I'll pay.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:11.37,1:09:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems like I'm a wanted man now.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:14.90,1:09:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:20.76,1:09:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I was really worried.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:22.60,1:09:24.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You almost got arrested.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:24.03,1:09:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I totally panicked.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:25.88,1:09:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to laugh about.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:28.18,1:09:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,This room is huge!
Dialogue: 1,1:09:29.43,1:09:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The bed's huge!
Dialogue: 1,1:09:30.43,1:09:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The bathroom's huge!
Dialogue: 1,1:09:35.24,1:09:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina. Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:36.94,1:09:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take a bath together.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:39.03,1:09:40.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Do it alone.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:41.50,1:09:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, let's take a\Nboys-only bath together.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:47.20,1:09:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so warm.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:49.95,1:09:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,1:09:54.40,1:09:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 1,1:09:54.89,1:09:56.96,Top,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:56.96,1:09:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Switch.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:59.74,1:10:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:01.71,1:10:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,1:10:02.88,1:10:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's try them all, Sempai.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:04.61,1:10:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,1:10:05.50,1:10:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I got severance pay.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:06.97,1:10:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina, we're having a\Ngorgeous dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:10.43,1:10:11.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:14.98,1:10:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:18.06,1:10:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:29.99,1:10:31.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:32.23,1:10:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me try that, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:35.00,1:10:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The curry's yummy.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:36.42,1:10:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yakisoba's delicious.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:37.85,1:10:39.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I want some too.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:39.50,1:10:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too early, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 1,1:10:41.63,1:10:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Tastes yummier if you\Nwait only two minutes.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:55.17,1:11:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear God, if you really exist, I beg you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:00.44,1:11:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is more than enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:02.42,1:11:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't need anything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:04.45,1:11:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll manage somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:07.82,1:11:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So please, don't give us anything more,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:12.44,1:11:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and don't take anything more from us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:16.50,1:11:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I beg you please, Dear God.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:20.29,1:11:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let us be together like this forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:11:26.78,1:11:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:28.30,1:11:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Happy 18th birthday.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:32.44,1:11:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's cheap, but I've picked\Nsomething that'd look good on you.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:39.56,1:11:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:44.75,1:11:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:46.30,1:11:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like this rain to stop?
Dialogue: 1,1:11:52.57,1:11:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:01.68,1:12:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I was chosen to be a human sacrifice.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:06.19,1:12:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsumi told me about\Nthe sunshine girl's fate.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:10.24,1:12:13.14,Main,,0,0,0,,She gets sacrificed and disappears,
Dialogue: 1,1:12:13.14,1:12:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,then the weather goes back to normal.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:17.31,1:12:18.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:18.35,1:12:23.86,Main,,0,0,0,,They're always telling weird stories.\NIt's not like people disappear...
Dialogue: 1,1:12:36.52,1:12:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 1,1:12:37.74,1:12:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking...
Dialogue: 1,1:12:44.75,1:12:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at you.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:48.66,1:12:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 1,1:12:53.99,1:12:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The more I pray for sunshine,\Nthe more my body becomes transparent.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:58.94,1:13:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that, if I die this way,
Dialogue: 1,1:13:01.73,1:13:05.02,Main,,0,0,0,,the usual summer will come back.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:05.74,1:13:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Take care of Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:06.76,1:13:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:08.17,1:13:11.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No way. You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:11.15,1:13:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll live together.\NThe three of us.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:13.05,1:13:14.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:14.22,1:13:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's make a promise, Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:17.62,1:13:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll always be together.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:21.37,1:13:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll work. I'll earn enough for all of us.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:24.57,1:13:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You quit the sunshine girl job.\NYour body will go back to normal.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:28.30,1:13:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 1,1:13:49.20,1:13:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:13:50.99,1:13:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was still on the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:01.29,1:14:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:02.91,1:14:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was rushing desperately,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:04.82,1:14:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}trying to reach the light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:09.08,1:14:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I thought I did,\NI reached a dead end instead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:14.42,1:14:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I decided I wanted to enter that light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:20.77,1:14:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And at the edge of it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:22.99,1:14:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:26.53,1:14:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:29.44,1:14:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day I met you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:33.94,1:14:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You looked like a lost kitten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:38.39,1:14:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you've found a meaning for my existence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:42.98,1:14:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I kept working as the sunshine girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:45.46,1:14:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'cos I was happy to make people smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:48.85,1:14:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really glad I've met you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:14:53.71,1:14:56.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, don't cry, Hodaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:15:12.54,1:15:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 1,1:15:17.29,1:15:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka...
Dialogue: 1,1:16:06.73,1:16:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:08.12,1:16:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:09.62,1:16:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:10.87,1:16:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:12.31,1:16:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:13.88,1:16:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina's disappeared.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:18.21,1:16:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I just dreamt...
Dialogue: 1,1:16:20.88,1:16:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,that she was disappearing in the sky.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:28.81,1:16:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 1,1:16:31.97,1:16:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Open the door.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:33.64,1:16:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 1,1:16:34.40,1:16:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:38.67,1:16:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka Morishima, right?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:40.40,1:16:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a missing person.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:43.53,1:16:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,And suspected of unlawful\Npossession of a weapon.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:47.07,1:16:48.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to the police station.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:48.37,1:16:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 1,1:16:49.41,1:16:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:49.41,1:16:51.42,Top,,0,0,0,,Let me go, I said!
Dialogue: 1,1:16:51.42,1:16:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:16:52.89,1:16:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sempai.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:53.69,1:16:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't struggle.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:08.97,1:17:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:14.91,1:17:19.50,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After months of rain, the Kanto plain is\Nfinally seeing some brilliant sunshine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:19.50,1:17:22.95,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems unreal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:22.95,1:17:24.95,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the last few hours, a sudden change in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:24.95,1:17:27.45,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By 8am. the temperature was already over 25°C.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:27.45,1:17:30.93,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Many areas around the Arakawa river are flooded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:30.93,1:17:32.83,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The transport system is still paralyzed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:32.83,1:17:35.43,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The extent of the damage has yet to be assessed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:35.43,1:17:38.46,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll take a few days at least for recovery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:38.46,1:17:42.22,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone looks happy under the clear blue sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:17:42.22,1:17:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at the sky.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:42.22,1:17:44.22,Top,,0,0,0,,Is it for real?
Dialogue: 1,1:17:44.22,1:17:46.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's sunny.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:44.22,1:17:46.22,Top,,0,0,0,,It cleared up!
Dialogue: 1,1:17:46.22,1:17:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky's so clear.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:48.22,1:17:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:49.99,1:17:53.26,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, real summer has arrived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:18:03.64,1:18:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:08.42,1:18:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina...
Dialogue: 1,1:18:10.73,1:18:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,...sacrificed herself.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:13.15,1:18:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina! Tell me it's not true!
Dialogue: 1,1:18:14.38,1:18:15.33,Top,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 1,1:18:15.33,1:18:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:18:21.36,1:18:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got a question.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:24.09,1:18:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl who was with you yesterday\Nis 15-year-old Hina Amano, right?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:31.29,1:18:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:34.21,1:18:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina's 15?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:37.56,1:18:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Not 18?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:39.59,1:18:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She faked her resume at work.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:43.39,1:18:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess she had to make a living,\Nbut she's still in middle school.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:46.86,1:18:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Compulsory school age.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:49.90,1:18:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:52.59,1:18:54.78,Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 1,1:18:54.78,1:18:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the oldest one.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:58.38,1:19:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:01.07,1:19:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you know where she may be?
Dialogue: 1,1:19:05.24,1:19:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky has cleared because\Nshe offered herself in exchange.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:10.89,1:19:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And nobody knows that...
Dialogue: 1,1:19:12.79,1:19:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:14.89,1:19:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a pain.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:17.02,1:19:18.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Will we need an expert medical witness?
Dialogue: 1,1:19:23.30,1:19:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's clear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:19:38.67,1:19:41.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Daddy! Did you look outside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:19:41.05,1:19:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:42.39,1:19:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dreamt of Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:19:45.20,1:19:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure it was her who\Nbrought the sunshine again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:19:52.16,1:19:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:54.09,1:19:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:59.38,1:20:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:00.19,1:20:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Detective, I've got a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:04.53,1:20:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,1:20:05.70,1:20:10.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go look for Hina.\NIt's my turn to help her now.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:10.70,1:20:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll come back as soon as I find her.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:12.67,1:20:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to you in here. Come on.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:18.33,1:20:21.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell Mr. Yasui we'll interrogate him now.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:21.10,1:20:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:23.46,1:20:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:27.99,1:20:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:29.88,1:20:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:32.14,1:20:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:36.37,1:20:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:36.37,1:20:38.73,Top,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get out of here.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:39.80,1:20:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:43.06,1:20:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:49.03,1:20:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:53.20,1:20:54.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:55.45,1:20:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Cheeky bastard.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:56.85,1:20:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Cross the street.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:57.43,1:20:58.33,Top,,0,0,0,,Yes Sir!
Dialogue: 1,1:21:05.34,1:21:06.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 1,1:21:15.39,1:21:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:19.35,1:21:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsumi?
Dialogue: 1,1:21:20.44,1:21:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,1:21:22.36,1:21:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:27.11,1:21:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Get on.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:34.36,1:21:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 1,1:21:36.95,1:21:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Nagi called.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:38.87,1:21:42.12,Main,,0,0,0,,He said Hina has disappeared\Nand you got arrested.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:42.12,1:21:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 1,1:21:43.36,1:21:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,At the Child Consultation Center.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:50.31,1:21:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,How exciting.
Dialogue: 1,1:21:51.58,1:21:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,We're outlaws now!
Dialogue: 1,1:21:55.28,1:21:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are we going, then?
Dialogue: 1,1:22:02.41,1:22:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Another visitor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:22:07.40,1:22:08.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, another girl.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:08.89,1:22:11.52,Main,,0,0,0,,He's popular.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:13.45,1:22:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:14.28,1:22:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ayane! You're here too.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:17.03,1:22:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Kana, this is Ayane.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:18.41,1:22:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:19.45,1:22:20.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ayane, this is Kana.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:20.75,1:22:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:21.68,1:22:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And she's officer Sasaki.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:23.58,1:22:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll be here with me all day.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:25.75,1:22:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're like a VIP, Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:28.50,1:22:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:30.98,1:22:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:33.05,1:22:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the sudden news.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:35.07,1:22:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Really! When I heard they took you\Ninto custody, my heart almost stopped.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:39.09,1:22:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Same for me.\NMy heart's still pounding.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:41.42,1:22:43.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Touch and feel it, Nagi.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:45.31,1:22:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:51.10,1:22:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:52.68,1:22:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,1:22:53.29,1:22:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my first visit.\NI'm a bit nervous.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:56.85,1:22:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,1:22:58.24,1:23:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I need the toilet.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:00.17,1:23:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:04.89,1:23:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I owe you one.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:06.41,1:23:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez. You even call your ex\Nwhen you need something.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:12.28,1:23:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:12.92,1:23:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Look the other way.\NI'll take my clothes off.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:26.26,1:23:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Keisuke Suga.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:28.19,1:23:29.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:29.54,1:23:31.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 1,1:23:31.31,1:23:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer's finally back\Nthe way it should, huh?
Dialogue: 1,1:23:35.81,1:23:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you I know nothing\Nabout that runaway boy.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:38.86,1:23:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we check out your office for a minute?
Dialogue: 1,1:23:40.90,1:23:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that for?
Dialogue: 1,1:23:41.79,1:23:43.95,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's flooded.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:43.95,1:23:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no one in there.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:47.54,1:23:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a bit embarrassing, but...
Dialogue: 1,1:23:51.21,1:23:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? He ran away?
Dialogue: 1,1:23:53.46,1:23:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the police station?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:23:56.14,1:23:57.47,Main,,0,0,0,,A derelict building in Yoyogi?
Dialogue: 1,1:23:57.47,1:24:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where she became a sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:59.68,1:24:00.97,Top,,0,0,0,,Bend down!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:02.38,1:24:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she got connected to the sky\Non the roof of that building.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:07.48,1:24:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So, if I go there, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 1,1:24:15.05,1:24:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:19.58,1:24:21.91,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,You, on that bike! Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:22.58,1:24:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold tight!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:31.43,1:24:33.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:33.00,1:24:34.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsumi!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:34.17,1:24:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I awesome or what?\NI think I was born for this.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:38.41,1:24:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 1,1:24:39.51,1:24:43.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...I should become a speed cop!
Dialogue: 1,1:24:43.27,1:24:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,They won't hire you now.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:49.38,1:24:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for the reason for his escape...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:24:53.27,1:24:57.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think he may be searching\Nfor the girl who was with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:24:57.78,1:25:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a strange story.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:01.03,1:25:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,He said she's disappeared in\Nexchange for this good weather.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:07.54,1:25:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 1,1:25:09.89,1:25:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:12.29,1:25:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,But, he's throwing his life away.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:17.67,1:25:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,And all because there's a girl\Nhe wants to meet so badly.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:22.68,1:25:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Makes me feel a bit envious.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:26.90,1:25:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,There's not much point in telling me that.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:34.00,1:25:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga, you...
Dialogue: 1,1:25:36.26,1:25:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,1:25:38.75,1:25:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 1,1:25:40.32,1:25:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,1:25:42.04,1:25:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you are...
Dialogue: 1,1:25:44.95,1:25:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...crying.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:55.89,1:25:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:59.21,1:26:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We're jumping in!
Dialogue: 1,1:26:12.23,1:26:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't go any further.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:13.56,1:26:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:19.20,1:26:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Natsumi.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:26.24,1:26:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:26:28.45,1:26:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 1,1:26:53.91,1:26:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:26:55.55,1:26:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina, Hina, Hina!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:26:58.80,1:26:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:00.50,1:27:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you there? Hina!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:06.04,1:27:07.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Hodaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:08.37,1:27:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll clear up now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:12.55,1:27:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:13.91,1:27:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've eaten that for dinner\Nthree nights in a row.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:16.25,1:27:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it hurt?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:17.08,1:27:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a runaway, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:18.58,1:27:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, you can't enjoy Tokyo with this rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:21.08,1:27:22.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Younger than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:22.59,1:27:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be 18 next month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:24.70,1:27:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should treat me with respect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:25.70,1:27:27.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you hungry, Hodaka?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:27.34,1:27:28.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sit there and relax.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:28.25,1:27:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do you like living in Tokyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:30.09,1:27:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:32.10,1:27:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't feel like I'm suffocating anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:35.15,1:27:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happy to hear that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:36.85,1:27:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in love with this sunshine girl job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:42.41,1:27:45.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Hodaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:27:47.86,1:27:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone got onto the tracks.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:50.36,1:27:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 1,1:27:51.62,1:27:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 1,1:27:52.37,1:27:54.12,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 1,1:27:54.12,1:27:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,1:27:55.79,1:27:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:28:00.29,1:28:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that? Hilarious.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:00.29,1:28:03.29,Top,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 1,1:28:03.29,1:28:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,There's someone running.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:03.29,1:28:05.62,Top,,0,0,0,,He'll get arrested.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:05.62,1:28:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,There are idiots like that.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:22.31,1:28:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:28:24.64,1:28:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Hina!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:28:26.18,1:28:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made you do that sunshine girl thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:28:28.26,1:28:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've shouldered all responsibility.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:28:31.81,1:28:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:28:32.57,1:28:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Hodaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:28:35.10,1:28:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would you like this rain to stop?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:29:06.01,1:29:07.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 1,1:29:07.96,1:29:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:10.49,1:29:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,1:29:11.29,1:29:14.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,1:29:14.27,1:29:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina's disappeared.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:16.45,1:29:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my fault. The sunshine\Ngirl job was my idea.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:19.67,1:29:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:20.66,1:29:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my turn to help her now!
Dialogue: 1,1:29:25.03,1:29:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I must go.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:27.37,1:29:28.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,1:29:28.21,1:29:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:29.15,1:29:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I can go to heaven through there!
Dialogue: 1,1:29:34.21,1:29:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 1,1:29:35.60,1:29:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,She's in the sky!\NI'll use the emergency stairs.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:38.72,1:29:42.38,Top,,0,0,0,,She can't be up there...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:38.72,1:29:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to help her!
Dialogue: 1,1:29:42.38,1:29:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 1,1:29:45.48,1:29:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:47.80,1:29:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back to the police station.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:49.83,1:29:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll understand.\NYou've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:53.48,1:29:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,If you keep running away, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:56.85,1:29:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You know that.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:58.49,1:30:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Suspect's car found.\NGoing to apprehend him.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:01.00,1:30:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\NI'll come with you.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:04.86,1:30:07.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's explain everything together, OK?
Dialogue: 1,1:30:07.17,1:30:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Please!
Dialogue: 1,1:30:08.44,1:30:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:10.50,1:30:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 1,1:30:12.05,1:30:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 1,1:30:18.01,1:30:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't stand in my way!
Dialogue: 1,1:30:21.63,1:30:23.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka. That's...
Dialogue: 1,1:30:23.46,1:30:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go see Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:48.91,1:30:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka Morishima.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:50.38,1:30:52.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Drop the gun.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:52.25,1:30:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:55.63,1:30:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:57.56,1:30:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll explain.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:59.16,1:31:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 1,1:31:02.14,1:31:03.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 1,1:31:03.89,1:31:06.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Put the gun down, Morishima.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:06.39,1:31:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't make me shoot.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:20.86,1:31:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:21.91,1:31:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on Hodaka,\Njust put it down.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:24.70,1:31:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 1,1:31:26.91,1:31:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid!
Dialogue: 1,1:31:28.41,1:31:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 1,1:31:29.92,1:31:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you holding me up?
Dialogue: 1,1:31:31.84,1:31:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You all know nothing.\NYou pretend you don't.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:35.22,1:31:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want to see her...
Dialogue: 1,1:31:38.93,1:31:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...once more!
Dialogue: 1,1:31:46.52,1:31:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 1,1:31:50.04,1:31:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 1,1:31:52.09,1:31:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Take your hands off Hodaka, assholes!
Dialogue: 1,1:31:57.86,1:31:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:00.11,1:32:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:05.05,1:32:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:07.09,1:32:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:09.57,1:32:10.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:12.07,1:32:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:13.03,1:32:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:16.63,1:32:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring my sister back!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:53.39,1:32:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear God,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:32:55.17,1:32:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}please, please, please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:32:58.92,1:33:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:33:30.35,1:33:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Sky fish?
Dialogue: 1,1:33:59.12,1:34:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:18.42,1:34:20.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:21.72,1:34:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:34.99,1:34:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:42.44,1:34:43.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:43.44,1:34:44.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:51.69,1:34:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:52.65,1:34:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:53.45,1:34:54.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:06.49,1:35:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:08.38,1:35:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka! Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:10.63,1:35:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of my hands.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:12.05,1:35:12.78,Main,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:30.81,1:35:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:31.91,1:35:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:40.19,1:35:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:42.34,1:35:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if I do, the weather will...
Dialogue: 1,1:35:45.95,1:35:47.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:47.84,1:35:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's enough.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:49.17,1:35:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be\Nthe sunshine girl anymore.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:05.30,1:36:08.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Who cares if we don't\Nsee the sunshine again.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:08.11,1:36:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you more than any blue sky.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:12.84,1:36:14.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The weather...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:14.54,1:36:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,...can stay crazy!
Dialogue: 1,1:36:56.12,1:36:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Pray for yourself...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:58.91,1:37:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,...Hina.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:01.66,1:37:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:22.19,1:37:23.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 1,1:38:09.14,1:38:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain started falling again\Nthat day, and never stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:13.92,1:38:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's slowly sinking Tokyo into the water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:18.42,1:38:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's still falling now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:20.58,1:38:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}three years later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:25.24,1:38:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How fast time flies, I can't believe\Nhow quickly the moments have passed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:31.66,1:38:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The precious years have come\Nand gone too soon, here with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:44.51,1:38:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've learned from you the right\Nway to do what must be done{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:38:59.54,1:39:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:06.54,1:39:07.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Morishima Sempai!
Dialogue: 1,1:39:10.10,1:39:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Er... You're moving to Tokyo, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,1:39:13.55,1:39:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:16.07,1:39:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, ask him.\NIt's now or never.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:19.15,1:39:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, possibly, this is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:21.91,1:39:23.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 1,1:39:23.62,1:39:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something\NI've always wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:26.76,1:39:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the first time someone\Ntells me they love me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:29.69,1:39:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know...
Dialogue: 1,1:39:32.72,1:39:33.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 1,1:39:33.65,1:39:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it true you're wanted\Nby the police in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 1,1:39:38.45,1:39:39.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,1:39:43.57,1:39:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That summer of three years ago,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:47.42,1:39:51.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was arrested and went on trial.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:51.01,1:39:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They put me on probation until graduation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:55.39,1:39:58.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The island, my parents'\Nhouse and the school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:39:58.42,1:40:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all were the same old places\Nwhere I was supposed to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:02.06,1:40:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, I just kept quietly\Nwaiting for graduation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:07.91,1:40:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:10.44,1:40:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...seen Hina since that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:15.46,1:40:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea what I'll think{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:18.45,1:40:23.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}seeing Tokyo after it changed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:23.37,1:40:26.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nor what I'll say to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:27.81,1:40:30.22,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow's weather for the Kanto region.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:30.22,1:40:32.38,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will rain again all day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:33.28,1:40:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I need to find a part-time job.
Dialogue: 1,1:40:42.14,1:40:47.95,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The high will be 15°C. Same or slightly\Nhotter than today in most areas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:40:49.25,1:40:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 1,1:40:50.64,1:40:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of part-time jobs...
Dialogue: 1,1:40:57.42,1:40:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's still there.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:04.62,1:41:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a sunshine girl request{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:41:07.61,1:41:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from two years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:41:09.58,1:41:13.53,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next stop Takashimadaira.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:41:13.53,1:41:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Look who's here.\NAre you alone?
Dialogue: 1,1:41:15.67,1:41:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's the sunshine girl?
Dialogue: 1,1:41:17.67,1:41:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,She's no longer a sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:21.17,1:41:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I came just to tell you that.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:25.34,1:41:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:28.10,1:41:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You moved.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:30.11,1:41:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You used to live in an older house downtown.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:32.70,1:41:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,The whole area is under water now.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:36.44,1:41:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:38.43,1:41:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you apologize?
Dialogue: 1,1:41:39.94,1:41:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 1,1:41:44.45,1:41:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, that area\Nused to be under the sea.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:50.10,1:41:53.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Until 200 years ago.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:54.71,1:41:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,In old times, Tokyo was just a bay.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:58.90,1:42:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Human beings and the weather\Nchanged it, little by little.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:04.36,1:42:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So, well... I think it's just\Ngone back to its original self.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:11.82,1:42:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:12.98,1:42:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been thinking about\Nthat crap for three years?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:15.48,1:42:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: 1,1:42:16.97,1:42:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You're about to start college,\Nbut you're still acting like a kid.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:20.93,1:42:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that day we...
Dialogue: 1,1:42:23.09,1:42:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You two caused this?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:25.29,1:42:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You changed the world?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:30.25,1:42:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:32.31,1:42:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter yourself, dummy.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:36.52,1:42:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, I went on a date with my daughter.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:39.25,1:42:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Natsumi and Nagi were in the way.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:42.71,1:42:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop brooding over stupid\Nstuff and go see her.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:47.29,1:42:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:48.84,1:42:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I was on probation.\NI didn't want to cause her trouble.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:52.49,1:42:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even have a cellphone.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:54.63,1:42:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:56.99,1:42:59.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say to her.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:04.54,1:43:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Rain? You're so big now.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:08.28,1:43:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, get out of here.\NGo now. I've got work to do!
Dialogue: 1,1:43:11.58,1:43:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Just go to her house.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:14.76,1:43:16.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:16.29,1:43:18.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Come back again.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:18.12,1:43:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:20.46,1:43:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, young man.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:23.96,1:43:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The world's always been crazy anyway.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:37.89,1:43:41.90,Broadcast,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next stop Hamamatsucho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:43:42.62,1:43:43.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You're super positive.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:43.91,1:43:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 1,1:43:44.62,1:43:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to the picnic.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:45.96,1:43:46.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 1,1:43:57.71,1:44:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It was under the sea.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:02.39,1:44:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,The world's always been crazy.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:08.63,1:44:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,So, it's no one's fault that it's like this.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:13.18,1:44:16.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this what I should say to her?
Dialogue: 1,1:44:48.27,1:44:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. That's not it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:44:51.08,1:44:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, I...\NWe changed the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:44:56.18,1:44:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made a choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:44:57.81,1:45:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've chosen her. I've chosen this world.\NI've chosen to live here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,1:45:02.44,1:45:03.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 1,1:45:09.08,1:45:09.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 1,1:45:17.67,1:45:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,1:45:19.41,1:45:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 1,1:45:23.37,1:45:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:24.73,1:45:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hina, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 1,1:45:28.13,1:45:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,180)}...we're gonna be OK.

